</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>POCO F4 GT 正式發佈　外形　功能　發售詳情　另加原神耳機 + 手錶</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/28/poco-f4-gt-budspro-genshinimpact-pocowatch/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=poco-f4-gt-budspro-genshinimpact-pocowatch</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Edward]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 28 Apr 2022 12:33:06 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[潮流手錶]]></category><category><![CDATA[音樂耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[Buds Pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[F4 GT]]></category><category><![CDATA[Poco]]></category><category><![CDATA[原神]]></category><category><![CDATA[小米 Watch S1 Active]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1097633</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>POCO 這個小米的 sub brand 一向以型格及高性價比主打，日前的發佈會，POCO 就終於推出年度旗艦 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>POCO 這個小米的 sub brand 一向以型格及高性價比主打，日前的發佈會，POCO 就終於推出年度旗艦手機 F4 GT，以及與著名手機遊戲《原神》合作推出的 Buds Pro 原神特別版及自家的 POCO Watch 智能手錶。究竟這 3 件新產品有甚麼特別之處？就讓 Edward 現在為大家介紹一下。</p><h2>POCO F4 GT：旗艦電競配置 + 超快充</h2><p>首先出場的，是 POCO 今年的旗艦之作 F4 GT，在設計上，它其實是 Redmi K50 電競版的國際版，配置了最新 Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 1 處理器、8GB / 12GB RAM 及 128GB / 256GB 儲存空間，可說是旗艦級的配置。另外，它的 6.67 吋熒幕除了採用了 AMOLED 材質，而且還支援 120Hz 高更新率，打機起來應該十分暢順。至於其他配置，包括：內建 6,400 萬像素主攝鏡 + 800 萬像素超廣角鏡及 200 萬像素微距鏡的主相機、2,000 萬像素前相機、支援 5G 網絡、內置 4 對稱設計喇叭單元（中高音 x 2 + 低音 x 2）及支援 Dolby Atmos 及 Hi-Res Audio 音效格式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_00_34-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097637" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_00_34-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_00_34-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_00_34-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_00_34-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_01_27-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097638" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_01_27-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_01_27-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_01_27-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_01_27-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>至於電競部分方面，POCO F4 GT 在機身上設有 2 個實體按鍵，當橫向打機時可自設不同功能，在玩射擊、格鬥或運動遊戲時十分有用。此外，它的喇叭擺位亦放在機身左右上方，令大家雙手打機時不會遮著喇叭出聲。另外，就連附送的 USB-C 線都採用 L 形設計，這樣即使邊打機邊充電，USB 線都不會頂著手掌不舒服。除此以外，F4 GT 內建了 3 個收音咪，在機身（橫向使用時）的左側、右側及下方，令大家與隊友打機時，可以清晰地互相以語音溝通討論戰術。散熱方面，F4 GT 亦採用了 LiquidCool 3.0 技術，設有兩塊超大合共 4860mm2 面積的散熱片，放在主要發熱的 SoC 及充電 ICs 上，令熱力發出後可以有效地即時散掉，不會因散熱不佳而對效能有所影響。最後值得一提的是，就是為了讓用家即使打機時都可以邊打邊充電，它支援 120W 超快速充電，隨機亦附送 120W 電壓輸出火牛，官方表示在閒置時，可以 17 分鐘將手機內的 4,700mAh 鋰電池由 0% 充電至 100%，即使打機時邊打邊充，亦可以在 27 分鐘將電量由 0% 充電至 100%，這樣大家就不用擔心打機時不夠電而需要暫停了。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_07_24-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097639" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_07_24-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_07_24-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_07_24-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_07_24-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_08_16-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097640" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_08_16-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_08_16-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_08_16-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_08_16-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_04_49-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097641" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_04_49-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_04_49-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_04_49-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-21_04_49-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_23_32-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097642" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_23_32-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_23_32-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_23_32-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_23_32-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>POCO F4 GT 設有黑色、銀灰色及黃色 3 色選擇，將會在即日至 5 月 7 日在指定國家接受預訂，而其他國家及地區（包括：香港）則會在稍後推出。定價方面，POCO F4 GT 設有 8 + 128 及 12 + 256 兩個版本，定價分別為 599 歐羅（約 HK$4,980）及 699 歐羅（約 HK$5,810）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_27_56-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097643" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_27_56-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_27_56-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_27_56-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_27_56-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_34_10-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097644" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_34_10-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_34_10-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_34_10-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_34_10-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_37_11-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097645" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_37_11-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_37_11-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_37_11-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_37_11-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>POCO Buds Pro 原神特別版：《原神》加持外形特別</h2><p>相信有玩開手機 ARPG 遊戲的讀者，應該都有聽過《原神》這款遊戲。而在日前的發佈會中，官方就宣佈推出 POCO 旗下的首款 IoT 產品（？）POCO Buds Pro 原神特別版。它在外形及功能上，基本上與 Redmi Buds 3 Pro 一模一樣，只是外形上加入了《原神》其中一個遊戲角色 Klee 的原素，充電盒採用了紅色外表淺啡色內籠的設計，加上全紅色的耳機單元，並印上 Klee 帽子上的標誌在耳機上，充滿著《原神》的元素。不只這樣，當打開耳機充電盒、連接手機時、甚至耳機無電時，Klee 都會發出聲音作出提示。而包裝盒設計亦十分漂亮，最特別是附送的耳機充電盒套，設計與 Klee 的揹包是一模一樣的，如果你是《原神》Klee 的支持者，這款 POCO Buds Pro 原神特別版應該會十分喜歡。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_06-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097646" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_06-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_06-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_06-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_06-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_59-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097647" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_59-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_59-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_59-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_59-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_20-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097648" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_20-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_20-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_20-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_40_20-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>發售詳情方面，POCO Buds Pro 原神特別版現已在部分國家推出，定價為 69 歐羅起（約 HK$573）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_43_31-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097649" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_43_31-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_43_31-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_43_31-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_43_31-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_43_50-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097650" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_43_50-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_43_50-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_43_50-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_43_50-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>POCO Watch：自家平價智能手錶</h2><p>最後一項當晚 POCO 推出的新產品，就是 POCO 旗下首隻智能手錶 POCO Watch。它的錶身設有藍、黑、金 3 色設計，而且可以按個人喜好替換不同顏色的錶帶，而且重量只有 31g，戴在手上應該頗為舒服。硬件上，POCO Watch 內建了 1.6 吋 320 x 360 解像度 AMOLED 熒幕，亦內建了光學心跳偵測器等，可為用家量度心跳、血氧等，而內建的其他感應器，更可讓大家在睡覺時作睡眠監測，方便知道自己的睡眠質素。它亦支援 5ATM 防水功能，即使戴著游水亦無問題，更內建了包括游泳、騎單車在內超過 100 種運動模式，方便大家在做不同運動時作紀錄用，而且它內建支援多種 GPS 系統，即使做運動時手機不在身上，亦可以準確紀錄所經過的地方，跑步、騎單車等運動時要紀錄路徑就十分方便了。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_44_40-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097651" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_44_40-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_44_40-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_44_40-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_44_40-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_45_20-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097652" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_45_20-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_45_20-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_45_20-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_45_20-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_47_22-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097653" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_47_22-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_47_22-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_47_22-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_47_22-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_47_43-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097654" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_47_43-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_47_43-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_47_43-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_47_43-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_48_28-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097655" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_48_28-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_48_28-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_48_28-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_48_28-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>至於電量方面，它內建了 225mAh 容量電池，官方表示在一般使用情況下，可為用家提供最多 14 日的使用時間，在智能手錶中算是長氣。發售詳情方面，POCO Watch 在部分國家即時推出發售，定價為 79 歐羅（約 HK$656），頗為抵玩。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_48_44-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097656" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_48_44-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_48_44-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_48_44-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_48_44-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_49_00-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_49_00-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_49_00-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_49_00-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/2022-04-26-20_49_00-POCO-F4-GT-Global-Launch-Event-YouTube.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
